title: Andrew Gwynne – 2022 Comments on Matt Hancock Going on I’m a Celebrity
author: admin
summary: The comments made by Andrew Gwynne, the Labour MP for Denton and Reddish, on Twitter on 1 November 2022.
content:
To be fair to Matt Hancock, I’d sooner eat wallaby anus than be a Tory MP too.
